surf_the_distance
--
Map by SKAR and blodey
Models by Black Sheep
--

This is a very long linear surf map made for 66 tick.

It takes roughly 4 minutes to surf through the map from start to end.

The map has many hidden secrets, it's up to you to find them all!

The map has an extreme amount of custom textures and sounds which is why the file has such a big size.
Totally worth the harddrive space though.
